---
title: Gettin’ Figgy With It Chicken with Roasted Brussels Sprouts & Mashed Potatoes
description: Na na na na na nana / Na na na na nana / Gettin’ figgy with it. Fig jam, that is! Here, we’ve paired it with balsamic vinegar and rich chicken stock to bring you a pan sauce that’ll get your taste buds grooving. It’s equal parts sweet, tangy, and savory—in other words, the perfect topping for pan-seared chicken cutlets. On the side, there’s creamy mashed potatoes and crisp roasted Brussels sprouts, making this a square meal that totally rocks out.
